### Enhancements

This version of the plugin now uses AWS' ability to automatically [delete inactive task definitions](https://aws.amazon.com/about-aws/whats-new/2023/02/amazon-ecs-deletion-inactive-task-definition-revisions/) immediately after agents are completed.

As a result the GoCD server now needs `ecs:DeleteTaskDefinitions` permission granted to the role/instance profile your GoCD server runs with (in addition to `ecs:DeregisterTaskDefinition` etc). This is _NOT_ required by the role the agents themselves use. See [the documentation](https://github.com/gocd/gocd-ecs-elastic-agent/blob/master/docs/installation.md#alternatively-configure-ecs-manually) for more details.

The plugin will not delete historical inactive task definitions created by GoCD within your account.
